[Nouns] mineral world, mineral kingdom; unorganized matter, inorganic matter, brute matter, inanimate matter.
[Science of the mineral kingdom] mineralogy, geology, geognosy, geoscopy; metallurgy, metallography; lithology; oryctology, oryctography.
[Verbs] turn to dust.
[Adjectives] inorganic, inanimate, inorganized; lithoidal; azoic; mineral.
